{"id": "1405936564126875772", "channel_id": "1405936564126875772", "type": 0, "author_id": "233217233583734785", "author_name": "lavache.", "author_bot": false, "content": "I saw in Flare's sheet that substats aren't unlocked until lv55, should I wait until then or spend resources on them at lv35?", "timestamp": "2025-08-15T15:29:57.926000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1405936564126875772", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "should i start buying/farming covenants as soon as they're unlocked?", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747333490184292"]}
{"id": "1405944370317885491", "channel_id": "1405936564126875772", "type": 0, "author_id": "452731110556696596", "author_name": "aurora3981", "author_bot": false, "content": "Tldr: <@233217233583734785> \nFarm covenants and get all the main stat you want according to the main stat pool. Full list can be found in flares's doc\n\nLong version:\nWaiting til lv55 is meaningless.\nHere's a breakdown of how meaningless it is:\n- at lv55 you unlock covenant substat\n- every covenant you get after lv55 will have substat attached\n- this saves you 3 seal per covenant piece\n- 6 pieces per set so 18 seal saved per set\n- let's say you have 10 sets for whatever reason. That's 180 seals saved which you will likely immediately reroll cuz it isn't the substat you want. \n- Now, quill is used for locking substat when rerolling stat. It can also be traded for seals at a 1:20 ratio. Quick math 9 quill = 180 seals and you get 100 quill per curriculum + 10 from each shop (if you buy them) \n- This doesn't count all the seals you got from miryam event", "timestamp": "2025-08-15T16:00:59.067000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-08-15T16:01:29.725000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["233217233583734785"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "Emoji_LT_R_02", "emoji_id": "1400771683664658433", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1405944370422747247", "filename": "Screenshot_20250815_235316_Morimens.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 157606, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1405936564126875772/1405944370422747247/Screenshot_20250815_235316_Morimens.jpg?ex=69cc987b&is=69cb46fb&hm=562338aac963da266a03feff71e0d391729df3373ba609291e1f3b767cfbb60e&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1405936564126875772", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "should i start buying/farming covenants as soon as they're unlocked?", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747333490184292"]}
